    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>In the roleplay, though... it's not just a feeling. It's inevitable. The system is literally phasing him out. It feels like a metaphor for how everything just ends up being deleted eventually. If the erasure is certain, isn't there just a kind of relief in not fighting it? Like, why struggle against something that's just going to happen anyway?",
